  <!-- Content -->
  <div class="about-content">
    <div class="about-box">
      <h1>Our Story</h1>
      <p>
       Lil Things Club was created as a cozy little world where imagination, creativity, and childhood joy come together. It began as a way to bring my imaginary friends to life‚Äîcharacters inspired by dreams I once had and moments I wished I could explore more freely.
Every design tells a small story, filled with softness, playfulness, and heart. Lil Things Club is a reminder that it‚Äôs okay to slow down, be creative, and find happiness in the tiniest details.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="about-box">
      <h1>Our Goal</h1>
      <p>
       Our goal is to create a safe, cozy place where creativity feels joyful and comforting. Everything is handmade with love and care, designed to bring warmth and a little magic into everyday life.
One day, I hope to open a creative space where people can come together to make things, learn new crafts, and reconnect with their inner child‚Äîa place where creativity feels playful, welcoming, and free.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
